      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i already talked to my doctor about the zolpidem and they just gave me the prescription. they didn't really say anything about the melatonin i was already taking. since melatonin is just a natural supplement and not a real drug, wouldn't it be fine to just take them at the same time? i just really need to sleep tonight.",
